---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Arc^ Project — Saltwater Irrigation" description="Saltwater Irrigation explores plasma-activated water for salinity resilience. See status, next steps, and safety expectations.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-20">
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-arkup-teal">Project scaffold</p>
    <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold">Saltwater Irrigation</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-muted">
      Plasma-activated water meets salt-stressed agriculture. We’re documenting how PAW interacts with salinity gradients, plant physiology, and soil microbiomes—starting with hardy coastal crops.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 pb-16">
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="space-y-4 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 text-sm text-muted">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Project status</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><span class="font-semibold text-white">Stage:</span> Draft exploration</li>
          <li><span class="font-semibold text-white">Last updated:</span> awaiting initial lab partners</li>
          <li><span class="font-semibold text-white">Lead:</span> Arc^ core team</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4 rounded-3xl border border-[#ffb703]/30 bg-[#ffb703]/10 p-6 text-sm text-[#ffeec7]">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Safety snapshot</h2>
        <p>
          Draft risk assessment in progress. Expect high-voltage plasma considerations, aerosolised brine, and UV exposure safeguards. Experiments restricted to compliant labs.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em]">Formal template coming soon</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 pb-20">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Immediate next steps</h2>
    <ul class="mt-6 list-disc space-y-3 pl-6 text-muted">
      <li>Outline PPE requirements and interlocks for small-scale PAW irrigation rigs.</li>
      <li>Co-design a measurement schema covering salinity, conductivity, plant health, and microbial shifts.</li>
      <li>Recruit comparison sites (greenhouse, field, hydroponic) to validate prototypes.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
